snippet.title: Beacon Pines - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Beacon Pines launches September 22nd, 2022!

A cute and creepy adventure game, coming to Xbox One, Xbox Game Pass, Nintendo Switch, Steam, and other PC stores.

Wishlist today:
Steam - https://bit.ly/Beacon_Pines
Xbox - https://bit.ly/BeaconPinesXbox
Switch - https://bit.ly/BeaconPinesSwitch
